{"body":"Fixes #4.\n\n## Summary\n- Replaced the demo deploy job's `peaceiris/actions-gh-pages` branch push with the official GitHub Pages artifact deployment flow: `configure-pages`, `upload-pages-artifact`, and `deploy-pages`.\n- Exposed the Pages deployment URL from the deploy job and made the GitHub Pages e2e job test that exact deployed URL.\n- Added workflow regression tests so the release workflow cannot silently return to `gh-pages` branch publishing for a workflow-sourced Pages site.\n- Added a case study with preserved logs/raw data and a template comparison across JS, Rust, Python, and C# pipeline templates.\n- Added CI/CD troubleshooting docs for the “deploy succeeded but Pages did not update” failure mode.\n\n## Reproduction and Root Cause\nThe failed run `25746871509` reported a successful `Deploy Demo to GitHub Pages` job while the later `E2E Tests (GitHub Pages)` job failed against `https://link-assistant.github.io/formal-ai` with 14 failures. The preserved repo Pages settings show `build_type: workflow`, but the old workflow only pushed `docs/demo` to the `gh-pages` branch. That branch push can succeed without creating or serving a Pages deployment for a workflow-sourced Pages site, which produced the false-positive deploy job.\n\nFull investigation and raw evidence are in `docs/case-studies/issue-4/README.md`.\n\n## Template Follow-up\nThe JS template already uses the official Pages artifact flow. The Rust template still has the same risky `peaceiris/actions-gh-pages` pattern for docs, so I filed an upstream template issue: https://github.com/link-foundation/rust-ai-driven-development-pipeline-template/issues/48\n\n## Verification\n- `cargo fmt --all -- --check`\n- `cargo test --test unit ci_cd::workflow_release`\n- `cargo test --all-features --verbose`\n- `cargo test --doc --verbose`\n- `cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features`\n- `rust-script scripts/check-file-size.rs`\n- `GITHUB_BASE_REF=main rust-script scripts/check-changelog-fragment.rs`\n- `GITHUB_EVENT_NAME=pull_request GITHUB_HEAD_REF=issue-4-1e8c9b0d59e2 GITHUB_BASE_REF=main rust-script scripts/check-version-modification.rs`\n- `GITHUB_EVENT_NAME=pull_request rust-script scripts/detect-code-changes.rs`\n- `ruby -e 'require \"yaml\"; YAML.load_file(\".github/workflows/release.yml\"); puts \"workflow yaml parsed\"'`\n- `npm ci` from `tests/e2e`\n- `npx playwright install chromium` from `tests/e2e`\n- `npx playwright test --config=playwright.local.config.js` from `tests/e2e` (14 passed)\n","commits":[{"authoredDate":"2026-05-12T16:33:03Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-05-12T16:33:03Z","messageBody":"Adding .gitkeep for PR creation (default mode).\nThis file will be removed when the task is complete.\n\nIssue: https://github.com/link-assistant/formal-ai/issues/4","messageHeadline":"Initial commit with task details","oid":"f8ed4a2dca30391670ce9e6c343d4e201d4a43c5"},{"authoredDate":"2026-05-12T17:00:38Z","authors":[{"email":"drakonard@gmail.com","id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE0MzE5MDQ=","login":"konard","name":"konard"}],"committedDate":"2026-05-12T17:00:38Z","messageBody":"","messageHeadline":"Fix GitHub Pages workflow deployment","oid":"07084db34c0b7ad092c5bc701334428249b31ea9"}],"files":[{"path":".github/workflows/release.yml","additions":29,"deletions":12,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".gitkeep","additions":2,"deletions":1,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":"Cargo.lock","additions":1,"deletions":1,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":"changelog.d/20260512_170000_fix_pages_workflow_deploy.md","additions":6,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-4/README.md","additions":137,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-4/raw-data/deployments.json","additions":1,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":"docs/case-studies/issue-4/raw-data/issue-4-comments.json","additions":1,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":